@startuml
participant "调度任务" as Job
participant "拍卖服务" as AuctionSvc
participant "订单服务" as OrderSvc
participant "支付服务" as PaymentSvc
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "第三方支付" as Pay
participant "通知服务" as Notify

Job -> AuctionSvc : 扫描到期活动
AuctionSvc -> DB : 关闭活动并判定结果
AuctionSvc -> OrderSvc : 触发生成订单
OrderSvc -> DB : 生成待支付订单
OrderSvc -> Notify : 发送待支付通知
PaymentSvc -> Pay : 发起支付
Pay -> PaymentSvc : 支付回调
PaymentSvc -> DB : 幂等更新支付和订单状态
PaymentSvc -> Notify : 发送支付结果通知
@enduml
